	"These features are required:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Movie recording and replay
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Movie rerecording (using quicksaves to undo part of the movie)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Good emulation quality
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" The emulator must work in Linux - either as native or with emulation such as Wine.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"These emulators have been considered and rejected:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" FCE-Ultra (lacks recording)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" VirtuaNES (doesn't work in Linux (not even with winex))
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Nesticle (bad quality, lacks rerecording, slow under Dosbox)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Nester (lacks recording, doesn't work in Linux)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" iNES (bad quality, lacks recording)
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"Famtasia just happens to work. Which is why I use it.
]p
